Text:
As is my usual procedure, I prioritize the HD encode until it has other seeders in the swarm.

At that time, I will proceed to the SD version.
First time commenting here, so a BIG thank you.  You are the reason I've been able to keep up with this show until I can get my hd satellite going in my new home.

I HAVE to give you this caveat. Saban Brands just had Rangercrew -- one of the more popular Power Rangers message boards -- remove all links to encodes of episodes. I get mine from elsewhere but the possibility exists that the same thing could happen there as well.

If it does happen, my torrents are done.

FYI, Nickelodeon made a late schedule change on Thursday and removed "Stroke of Fate" from the schedule of Oct. 20.

As of right now, the Halloween-themed episode is still scheduled for Oct. 27. After that, who knows?
That's weird.  They removed Stroke of Fate, but are still playing the Halloween episode.  I wonder how that's gonna work out.
So that's why RangerBoard made the Multimedia section need 200 posts to view! They are afraid Saban will see it.
